<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="rub-vt">rub <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rʌb/    美 /rʌb/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>擦；摩擦；揉；搓：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>rub one’s eyes / hands / head 
揉眼睛/搓手/摸头</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>用...擦 / 涂；抹：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>rub sun cream on 
在…上涂防晒霜</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>磨；磨损 / 痛：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The back of my shoe is rubbing. 
我的鞋后跟磨脚。</p></div></div>